"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-golf-1932119-Jon-Rahm-LIV-Golf-2024-Olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Jon Rahmhas been accused of suffering one of the 'biggest chokes' of the year after blowing a final round lead at the2024 Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 139, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 124, \"end\": 138, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Spaniard had a four stroke lead after 10 holes on Sunday afternoon, only to capitulate in the closing stages as Scottie Scheffler\\u00a0came\\u00a0through to take gold.\", \"from\": 140, \"to\": 300, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 140, \"end\": 152, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Spaniard_(film)\", \"score\": 0.7999966551257347, \"rank\": 0.2500000000000275, \"text\": \"The Spaniard\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q11424\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Spaniard_(film)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Spaniard_(film)\"}, {\"begin\": 256, \"end\": 273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottie_Scheffler\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Scottie Scheffler\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottie_Scheffler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottie_Scheffler\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The American finished 19-under par, one shot clear of Team GB's Tommy Fleetwood, while Hideki Matsuyama took bronze after ending 17-under.\", \"from\": 302, \"to\": 440, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 306, \"end\": 314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999795554688, \"rank\": 9.823357702747333e-09, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 356, \"end\": 363, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.974086592333388, \"rank\": 0.026601497323763025, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 366, \"end\": 381, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tommy_Fleetwood\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tommy Fleetwood\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tommy_Fleetwood\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tommy_Fleetwood\"}, {\"begin\": 389, \"end\": 405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hideki_Matsuyama\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hideki Matsuyama\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hideki_Matsuyama\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hideki_Matsuyama\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rahm however, could only take fifth place on 15-under after his 71 at Le Golf National.\", \"from\": 442, \"to\": 529, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TheLIV Golfplayer cut a disconsolate figure afterwards, and the Golf Channel's Brandel Chamblee was merciless in his assessment of the 29-year-old.\", \"from\": 531, \"to\": 678, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Chamblee, a vociferous critic of the Saudi-backed tour, implied Rahm would rue his failure to take gold.\", \"from\": 679, \"to\": 783, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 679, \"end\": 687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chamblee,_Georgia\", \"score\": 0.9935874826063947, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chamblee\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chamblee,_Georgia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chamblee,_Georgia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Scottie Scheffler six back on the turn and wins gold without a play off,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 785, \"to\": 868, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"One shoots 29 and Jon Rahm shoots 39.\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 907, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 888, \"end\": 896, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jon_Rahm\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jon Rahm\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jon_Rahm\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jon_Rahm\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am going to put that down as one of the biggest collapses, chokes of the year.\\\"\", \"from\": 908, \"to\": 989, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Chamblee even referenced the heartbreak of one of Rahm's Ryder Cup team-mates, citing the\\u00a0misery thatRory McIlroysuffered in Pinehurst in June, when hemissed a short putt on the final hole to hand victory to Bryson DeChambeau.\", \"from\": 991, \"to\": 1217, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1206, \"end\": 1216, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryson_DeChambeau\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"DeChambeau\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryson_DeChambeau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryson_DeChambeau\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He added: \\\"That was right up there with Rory McIlroy at the US Open.\\\"\", \"from\": 1218, \"to\": 1287, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1258, \"end\": 1270, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rory_McIlroy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rory McIlroy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rory_McIlroy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rory_McIlroy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Discovery+is the new home of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1333, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The streamer is set to broadcast 3,800 hours of sport live from Paris.\", \"from\": 1334, \"to\": 1404, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1398, \"end\": 1403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999904503, \"rank\": 9.680254529969741e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports fans can getDiscovery+ for \\u00a33.99a month until the end of 2024 via Amazon Prime's video channels.\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1509, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1479, \"end\": 1491, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"score\": 0.9996546444215144, \"rank\": 0.0003454748405597101, \"text\": \"Amazon Prime\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This also comes with anAmazon Prime 30-day free trial.\", \"from\": 1510, \"to\": 1564, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Rahm himself also pulled no punches with his self-assessment, after enduring four bogeys and a double bogey in the final eight holes.\", \"from\": 1566, \"to\": 1699, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I not only feel like I let myself down but to just not get it done for the whole country of Spain, it's a lot more painful than I would like it to be,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1861, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1793, \"end\": 1798, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9214670275920599, \"rank\": 0.0849791783265526, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have gotten the question, where this tournament would rank in my opinion or what I would think it would feel like to win?\", \"from\": 1863, \"to\": 1987, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I think by losing today, I am getting a much deeper appreciation of what this tournament means to me than if I had won any medal, right.\", \"from\": 1988, \"to\": 2128, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am getting a taste of how much it really mattered.\", \"from\": 2130, \"to\": 2183, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have been very honoured to represent Spain in many, many different events, and to not get this one done stings quite a bit.\\\"\", \"from\": 2184, \"to\": 2310, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2223, \"end\": 2228, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9214670275920599, \"rank\": 0.0849791783265526, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2312, \"to\": 2421, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2422, \"to\": 2498, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2531, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  Chamblee, 62, has previously made no secret of his disdain for LIV Golf, so his willingness to take aim at Rahm will not come as a surprise.\", \"from\": 2532, \"to\": 2696, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2619, \"end\": 2627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LIV_Golf\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LIV Golf\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LIV_Golf\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LIV_Golf\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The American, a former professional golfer himself, has previously said that playing 54-hole tournaments was adversely affecting rebel players when they competed in major events.\", \"from\": 2697, \"to\": 2875, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2701, \"end\": 2709, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999795554688, \"rank\": 9.823357702747333e-09, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is a relatively small sample size given LIV has been playing for less than three years,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2877, \"to\": 2978, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2921, \"end\": 2924, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Super_Bowl_LIV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.780663852061686e-15, \"text\": \"LIV\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Super_Bowl_LIV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Super_Bowl_LIV\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But it's safe to say that LIV Golf, has been detrimental to the competitiveness of their careers when they compete at the highest level.\\\"\", \"from\": 2979, \"to\": 3117, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3006, \"end\": 3014, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LIV_Golf\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LIV Golf\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LIV_Golf\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LIV_Golf\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 3119, \"to\": 3288, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3256, \"end\": 3269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.7052471796046065e-18, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Expres